    <para id="id93089"><m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mrow/></m:math> If we use a linear, time invariant system with only poles, we can model the output as a recursive average as shown.</para>
    <equation id="id93099">
      <m:math overflow="scroll" mode="display">
        <m:mrow>
          <m:mi>y</m:mi>
