    <para id="id93166">Statisticians often refer to a model of the following form as an autoregressive process. Note that it has the same form as our equation above.</para>
    <equation id="id93172">
      <m:math overflow="scroll" mode="display">
        <m:mrow>
          <m:msub>
            <m:mi>Y</m:mi>
